The reason you agreed to be
the case's defense lawyer is because

35
00:02:11,231 --> 00:02:14,400
you suspect it's related to
the case 11 years ago, right?

36
00:02:15,535 --> 00:02:19,606
But to the police and the prosecutors,
the case is closed.

37
00:02:19,672 --> 00:02:22,775
You're doing this now
just to satisfy yourself, aren't you?

38
00:02:22,842 --> 00:02:25,745
