48
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:14,027
Miss Wakura?

49
00:03:15,528 --> 00:03:16,829
Mr. Kurokawa.

50
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:20,700
Thank goodness, you've opened your eyes.

51
00:03:21,968 --> 00:03:23,803
I had a horrible nightmare.

52
00:03:25,438 --> 00:03:28,007
<i>Your pile of books and files</i>

53
00:03:28,074 --> 00:03:31,311
<i>kept falling onto my desk.</i>

54
00:03:32,478 --> 00:03:37,684
I had no idea I was unconsciously
stressed out by that.

55
00:03:40,386 --> 00:03:41,221
I'm sorry.

56
00:03:43,823 --> 00:03:44,991
And…

57
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:48,695
Why are you holding my hand?

58
00:03:57,203 --> 00:03:58,438
I am really sorry.

59
00:03:59,772 --> 00:04:01,708
HOSHUNDO LAW OFFICE

60
00:04:03,042 --> 00:04:05,745
Miss Arima, it isn't your fault.

61
00:04:05,812 --> 00:04:09,048
