but they're Ayaka Akiu's
and Daisuke Asama's blogs.

76
00:04:54,594 --> 00:04:55,528
ASAMA'S RUINS TOUR

77
00:04:56,596 --> 00:04:57,797
KOOZ: I WILL GO THERE NEXT TIME.

78
00:04:57,864 --> 00:04:59,032
AYAKA'S DIARY

