518
00:30:49,647 --> 00:30:52,016
not due to the lack of ability
to inspect or the lack of evidence.

519
00:30:52,584 --> 00:30:56,387
It's caused by prejudice,
assumption, and useless dignity,

520
00:30:56,454 --> 00:30:58,690
the weakness and ugliness
of people's hearts.

521
00:30:59,557 --> 00:31:01,759
No matter how advanced
forensic science gets,

522
00:31:01,826 --> 00:31:04,495
it's pointless if the people
who use it are corrupt.

523
00:31:07,732 --> 00:31:08,900
What we need is

524
00:31:09,701 --> 00:31:13,938
the simple and honest will-power
to seek the truth.

525
00:31:16,541 --> 00:31:17,675
Without that,

526
00:31:18,710 --> 00:31:20,044
the victim's resentment

527
00:31:21,145 --> 00:31:23,348
and the agony
that the victim's family suffer

528
00:31:25,383 --> 00:31:29,320
will never be able to be settled
in the real sense.

529
00:31:32,991 --> 00:31:34,125
That was the case for the prosecution.

530
00:31:35,193 --> 00:31:36,027
Thank you.

531
00:31:36,094 --> 00:31:37,862
Please call the next witness.

532
00:31:53,478 --> 00:31:54,746
I swear that…

533
00:31:55,580 --> 00:32:00,018
