Kyoka Hanamaki and Nana Yamashiro.

559
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:27,005
He admits to all the crimes?

560
00:33:27,071 --> 00:33:28,606
Why did you do that?

561
00:33:30,675 --> 00:33:33,911
If I must say, it was to reveal

562
00:33:33,978 --> 00:33:37,148
the problem of Japan's police
and public prosecutors' office.

563
00:33:38,349 --> 00:33:40,551
I came up with the idea 11 years ago.

564
00:33:40,618 --> 00:33:43,654
If I plant evidence that points directly
to someone as the murderer

565
00:33:43,721 --> 00:33:45,623
and go to kill someone,

566
00:33:45,690 --> 00:33:47,358
what would you guys do?

567
00:33:48,826 --> 00:33:52,030
<i>I carefully selected the person</i>
<i>I would kill and the culprit.</i>

568
00:33:57,335 --> 00:33:58,436
<i>Put the bait there.</i>

