570
00:34:06,144 --> 00:34:08,446
I thought, they would find out
at once anyway.

571
00:34:09,847 --> 00:34:14,285
But the result was
you guys simply took the bait.

572
00:34:15,686 --> 00:34:18,022
So, I did it again,

573
00:34:18,089 --> 00:34:21,426
using Kyoka Hanamaki
and the stalker there.

574
00:34:23,761 --> 00:34:27,765
