<i>and let the stalker find it.</i>

575
00:34:31,436 --> 00:34:33,104
<i>I took the sketchbook</i>

576
00:34:33,171 --> 00:34:36,140
<i>from the crime scene to the factory</i>
<i>and threw it away.</i>

577
00:34:37,942 --> 00:34:41,379
The only thing that went wrong
was someone saw me.

578
00:34:41,446 --> 00:34:43,114
The kid, Nana Yamashiro.

579
00:34:43,948 --> 00:34:45,983
