so you killed her to shut her up?

580
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:47,085
No.

581
00:34:47,618 --> 00:34:50,822
The idiot shamelessly showed up
in front of me

582
00:34:50,888 --> 00:34:53,758
and told me to give her hush money.
That's why.

583
00:34:54,792 --> 00:34:57,028
I did feel sorry for the stalker.

584
00:34:57,095 --> 00:34:59,297
She was killed in the same way,

585
00:34:59,363 --> 00:35:02,166
so they suspected that
you were a serial killer.

586
00:35:02,967 --> 00:35:06,370
No wonder false convictions
still exist in this country.

587
00:35:11,809 --> 00:35:15,713
I've been able to say everything
and I feel amazing now.

588
00:35:16,747 --> 00:35:21,085
The press will make a fuss
and I'll become famous tomorrow.

589
00:35:21,686 --> 00:35:25,590
"The vicious serial killer confessed
his crime in court," they'll say.

590
00:35:27,358 --> 00:35:29,594
I'll be sentenced to death anyway.

591
00:35:30,761 --> 00:35:31,829
If you like,

592
00:35:31,896 --> 00:35:35,600
I'll tell you in detail
how I killed the women.

593
00:35:36,501 --> 00:35:37,468
Mr. Akiu!

594
00:35:43,641 --> 00:35:45,877
Good Lord, my work was amazing!

595
00:35:46,677 --> 00:35:49,580
The useless police, prosecutors.

596
00:35:49,647 --> 00:35:51,182
In your faces!

597
00:35:55,286 --> 00:35:57,955
Kazunari Kozu, 35 years old.

598
00:36:00,558 --> 00:36:03,227
Your father is a renowned pathologist.

599
00:36:03,294 --> 00:36:06,430
You applied to Touo University's
Medical Department to do pathology

600
