but failed four times.

601
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:09,567
What?

602
00:36:09,634 --> 00:36:10,801
After the four years,

603
00:36:10,868 --> 00:36:13,738
you finally passed the exam,
but just before your enrolment

604
00:36:13,804 --> 00:36:16,240
