613
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:41,465
I went to meet the woman
who accused you of molestation.

614
00:36:43,234 --> 00:36:45,469
She regretted it very much.

615
00:36:47,405 --> 00:36:49,674
She lied and accused you of molestation

616
