685
00:42:22,206 --> 00:42:23,140
True.

686
00:42:24,475 --> 00:42:28,245
But at least I feel better now.

687
00:42:32,950 --> 00:42:34,218
I can now…

688
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:39,456
mourn over the death of Ayaka and Asama,

689
00:42:40,357 --> 00:42:41,392
the person she loved.

690
00:42:45,062 --> 00:42:46,163
Yeah.

691
00:42:57,207 --> 00:42:58,742
Why do you follow me?

692
00:42:58,809 --> 00:43:01,679
What? You go for a drink
at a time like this.

693
00:43:01,745 --> 00:43:04,548
But I'm telling you,
I'm going to have Oolong tea.

694
00:43:09,353 --> 00:43:13,824
I want to file an appeal for the retrial
of the murder 11 years ago.

695
00:43:14,959 --> 00:43:17,928
A public prosecutor has the right
to do so, indeed, but…

696
00:43:19,430 --> 00:43:23,133
One needs to correct his mistake.

697
00:43:30,341 --> 00:43:31,775
Good evening, dear.

698
00:43:34,812 --> 00:43:35,579
UNREAD - CRIMINAL DEFENSE
