Calm down. A young man
who aims to be a lawyer

704
00:43:48,459 --> 00:43:51,161
because he wants to handle
criminal cases has shown up.

705
00:43:51,228 --> 00:43:55,466
Someone who is going to bring us
even more trouble than Kurokawa.

706
00:43:55,532 --> 00:43:56,467
PASS

707
00:43:56,533 --> 00:43:57,668
Have some tea.

708
00:43:57,735 --> 00:43:59,403
Thank you.

