712
00:44:08,946 --> 00:44:11,382
-Really?
-After I pass it,

713
00:44:11,448 --> 00:44:15,519
I can help Mr. Kurokawa
on many, many more things.

714
00:44:15,586 --> 00:44:18,622
I am going to work much, much harder too.

